<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM4.7.2">
<l>koḷḷa māḷā viṉpa veḷḷaṅ kōtila tantiṭumeṉ</l>
<l>vaḷḷa lēyō vaiyaṅ koṇṭa vāmaṉā vōveṉṟeṉṟu</l>
<l>naḷḷi rāvu naṇpakalu nāṉirun tōla miṭṭāl</l>
<l>kaḷḷa māyā vuṉṉai yeṉkaṇ kāṇavan tīyāyē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Saying [and] saying “is he my benefactor who gives without fail</l>
<l>a flood of pleasure that does not die when taken, is he the dwarf who took the world?”,</l>
<l>if by full night and day I sit [and] make a noise/an appeal,</l>
<l>fraudulent trickster, won’t you graciously come so that my eyes see you?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
